long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Reliance Transcribing powered by TheRelianceHub is an advanced transcription tool that flawlessly converts the audio of your online meetings into correct text reports. Be it Google Meet-or soon Zoom and Microsoft Teams-Reliance Transcribing makes sure every detail of your conversation gets captured and transcribed with precision.

Key features include:

Online meeting transcription in real time.
Securely processed with SOC-2 and ISO 27002 protocols, so your data remains private.
Automatic delivery of reports right into your inbox after each session.
No storage of data: All audios and transcriptions are deleted immediately after delivery, hence keeping all your information very safe.
Reliance Transcribing caters to those professionals who demand security, efficiency, and accuracy.
